text.section:
A person may not drink any alcoholic beverage, as defined in this article, while:
On public property, unless authorized by a governmental entity that has jurisdiction over the property;
On the mall, adjacent parking area, or other outside area of any combination of privately owned retail establishments, like a shopping center, where the general public is invited for business purposes, unless authorized by the owner of the shopping center;
On an adjacent parking area or other outside area of any other retail establishment, unless authorized by the owner of the establishment; or
In any parked vehicle located on any of the places enumerated in this subsection, unless authorized.
